# Always: Error Learning Trigger

If any of these happen, load `project-esti-error-learning-agent.mdc` or skill `error-learning-1c`:

- `check_1c_code` / `review_1c_code` failed;
- `v8std` diagnostic appears;
- runtime/deploy/test failed;
- user invokes `capture-error` or `reflect-lesson`;
- the same mistake appears again;
- risky CFE/base-config change was attempted.

Do not create a new `.mdc` rule for one-off issues. Store first in reflection/L1 memory; promote only if repeated or critical.
